quran[50]{c,v,t}:
  15,50,U aâaqeb iW d aâaqeb aqeôêan
  15,51,Xebbeô iten $ef inebgawen n Ibôahim
  15,52,"Mi kecmen $uôes, nnan: \"tifrat\"! Inna: \"s tidep, nugad ikwen"
  15,53,"Nnan: \"ur ppagwad, a k nbecceô kan, s uqcic amusnaw"
  15,54,"Inna: \"tbecceôm iyi d, mi wessre$. Acu iyi d tbeccôem"
  15,55,"Nnan: \"Nbecceô ik id, s tidep, ur ppili seg wid iuysen"
  15,56,"Inna: \"anwa iuysen aêunu n Mass is, siwa im$eôôqen"
  15,57,"Inna: \"d acu ay d lmeqsud nnwen, a yimceggâen"
  15,58,"Nnan: \"Nekwni, s tidep, neppuceggaâ d s agdud ibe$wviyen"
  15,59,"Kkes ed tawacult n Luî, ara nsellek akw"
  15,60,"siwa tameîîut is. Ih, Nseyya a ppili, neppat, seg ineggura"
  15,61,Mi ôuêen imceggâen ar twacult n Luî
  15,62,"inna: \"kunwi, s tidep, d imdanen ur nessin"
  15,63,"Nnan: \"xaîi, Nusa d, $uôek, s wayen rran di ccekk"
  15,64,"Nusa d, $uôek, s tidep. Nekwni, war ccekk, nessawal tidep"
  15,65,"Öuê akked twacult ik, mi mazal yiv. Ddu deffir sen. Ur d itezzi yiwen degwen! Âaddit anda i wen ippunefk lameô"
  15,66,"Nseyya yas lameô agi: a d gwrin ad pwagezmen wakali"
  15,67,"Usan d, imezda$ n temdint, feôêen"
  15,68,"Inna: \"wigi, s tidep, d inebgawen iw, ur iyi cmmatet"
  15,69,"Ëezbet i Öebbi, ur iyi sdullut"
  15,70,"Nnan: \"day ur ak negdil ara imdanen"
  15,71,"Inna: \"atent an issi, ma taânam"
  15,72,"S tudert ik, ar ddebdeben si ssekôan nnsen"
  15,73,"Iwwet iten usu$u, tafrara"
  15,74,Nesrewt ip. Nesse$li d fellasen ageffur n yiéôa n talaxt
  15,75,"Deg waya, s tidep, d issekniyen i wid issnen ad ssikden"
  15,76,"Apan, ih, deg ubrid n yal ass"
  15,77,"Deg waya, s tidep, d assekni i lmumnin"
  15,78,"Ih, llan At Teégi, war ccekk, d imednas"
  15,79,"Nerra d ppaô segsen. Ihi, atent an, snat nni, deg ubrid ibanen"
  15,80,Ni$ At Lêioô skaddben imazanen
  15,81,Nebbwi yasen d issekniyen nne£. Wexxôen asen
  15,82,"Llan qqazen ixxamen n laman, deg idurar"
  15,83,"Iwwet iten usu$u, taûebêit"
  15,84,Ulay sen ixdem wayen la keppben
  15,85,"Ur Nexliq tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, siwa s tidep. Imir a d ias, war ccekk. Ihi, ssuref s lekyasa"
  15,86,"Ih, Mass ik d Axellaq, d Amusnaw"
  15,87,"Ni$ Nefka yak d ûa i usniles, akked Leqwôan ameqwôaêan"
  15,88,Ur pmuqul ar wayen is N$at kra n twaculin nnsen. Ur $webbel ilmend nnsen. Zger tacvaî ik $ef lmumnin
  15,89,"Ini: \"nekkini, s tidep, d aneddaô ipbegginen"
  15,90,Akken id Nessers i wid ibvan
  15,91,i irran Leqwôan d iêricen
  15,92,"S Mass ik, ard a ten Nesteqsi akw"
  15,93,ef wayen xeddmen
  15,94,"Ihi, emdeê ayen i$ef i k ippunefk lameô, îixxeô i imcurak"
  15,95,"Ih, a k Nqennaâ mgal wid ittihin"
  15,96,"i irran ôebbi nniven, ar tama n Öebbi. Deqqal ad éôen"
  15,97,"Ni$ Neéôa ar ul ik, keçç, iaâûeô seg wayen qqaôen"
  15,98,Sbuccaâ Mass ik s ccekôan. Ili seg wid ikennun
  15,99,"Aâbed Mass ik, ar k id ias utebbet"